{
  "stem": "18474.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that's-- that was afterwards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After that incident--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto was created.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the ghetto was created at the beginning of 1942.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I very little in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to come and stay a few days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father lived in the ghetto, my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sisters, they were young kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to take care of the cows for different farmers, you know, in pasture.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was their job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father later on became a-- a driver.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were horsemen, you know, we knew a lot about horses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they-- the Judenrat, they came to the Judenrat and they asked them, can they supply somebody who knows how to really handle horses.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the Judenrat picked my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was working on farms, different places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they made him for the driver.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He used to drive around the Germans to different villages, wherever they had to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was his job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he had the right to drive and out of the ghetto because he used to keep the horses in our stable, which was in-- inside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was the messenger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Anything was going on outside, because we had very little communications with anybody, if-- he was the messenger before the holes were dug-- dug up already, which a lot of people knew.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Ukrainians, they used to tell him that they're digging holes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he brought in the news and that's-- he was the-- the-- the-- the-- the communication man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that's-- that's the way it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stood-- our house fell into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Reuben.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he worked outside the ghetto as a-- what do you call them, a toolmaker in a-- in a shop which was run by a Czech.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
